<p>To make it easy to manage folder and items on web-based application, I developed a new open source project <a href="https://bitbucket.org/victorlin/treeview">Treeview</a>.</p>

<p><img src="http://user-image.logdown.io/user/822/blog/819/post/142555/ABbe16wTN7LpYRCFQQZA_%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2013-02-18-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.25.56.png" alt="螢幕快照-2013-02-18-上午11.25.56.png"></p>

<p>It makes folders and items in a web-based tree become draggable. You can see the <a href="http://victorlin.bitbucket.org/treeview/demo.html">online demo</a>. It's under the MIT license, feel free to use it or fork it.</p>